    "body": "The only possible way to make devtools work without loading any URL is to always load `about:blink` by default, but it would then causes troubles for apps because when navigating to other pages white flash would happen. So I'm afraid this is something that we won't do.\n\nFor learners, the simplest way is to explore the default app, it provides many nice little features for learning Electron. You can run `electron -h` to learn more.\n"
